<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two blocks: a (in two pieces) <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.98</measure>, marked <foreign lang="grc">ΓΑ</foreign> ; b <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">1.27</measure>, marked <foreign lang="grc">ΔΑ</foreign>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in two lines on the fascia, which has an extra moulding above the text, only here.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>-<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>; dot for stop; Diaresis; on first A of ἀναθέντα, l.1. Ligatures: ΗΜ, l.1, ΝΝ, l.2;.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0200" exact="none">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">institutions</rs>)</p>
</div>
